unikl.disco.numbers

Class Num

  • java.lang.Object
    • unikl.disco.numbers.Num
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NumDouble, NumFraction

    public abstract class Num
extends java.lang.Object
    Class emulating multiple dispatch (Java only offers single dispatch) in order to allow the user to switch between available number representations.
    Author:
    Steffen Bondorf
